  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeneratedFactory
    A class that serves as the entry point to the generated code providing access to existing individuals in the ontology and the ability to create new individuals in the ontology.
    Vocabulary
    Vocabulary class to provide access to the Manchester OWL API representatives for various entities in the ontology used to generate this code.
